        Changelog
        =========
        
        0.1 (2014-03-05)
        ----------------
        
        - Initial release.
        - Added dependency to Products.PloneFormGen, collective.contentleadimage and plone.app.theming.
        - Configure Plone email settings.
        - Enable sitemap.xml.gz and DC metadata.
        
